HoboSerenity
============

Testing plugin for Hobo + Serenity integration



Installation
============

script/plugin install git://github.com/iox/hobo-serenity.git



Example
=======
ordens.rb:
def  nombre_informe
  return "DOC-" + id
end
def after_save
  generar_informe
end


Example: Using download buttons
===============================
show.dryml:
<include src="/taglibs/hobo-serenity"/>
<show-page>
<append-heading:>
<informe-botones/>
</append-heading:>
</show-page>



Example: Regenerating a report after child update
=================================================
pedidos.rb:
def after_save
   orden.generar_informe
end
    
    
    
